name: Full Resolution
description:
Inspired by 80s synthwave vibe, I recorded this track using Korg analog synthesizers and some drum samples. All the patches was designed by me and tuned to A=432hz for a different experience.
For the cover did some basic coding on hydra. This is the second of 5 tracks i'll release soon exclusive as NFT.

This is the second piece of my EP "pixelate" 2/5. 
It called "Full Resolution". Recorded in A=432hz

Gear for this track
            Korg Minilogue - synth
            Tascam porta07 mini studio - tape recorder
            SSL2+ - audiobox
            Ableton Live 11
